# dbt build artifacts: never bake compiled SQL, manifests, or installed
# packages into the image. A stale `target/` in the build context poisons
# dbt's partial-parse cache so sources compile against an old schema (e.g.
# `raw.stations` instead of `ref.stations`), failing every run.
dbt/target
dbt/dbt_packages
dbt/logs
dbt/.user.yml
